## 🚀 How to Use

```bash
cd "Azure- 204"
dotnet run
```

Then select:
- **Option 1** → Azure App Service (6 demos)
- **Option 2** → Azure Functions (12 demos)
- **Option 3** → Azure Container Instances (7 demos) ⭐ NEW!
- **Option 4** → Azure Kubernetes Service (8 demos) ⭐ NEW!

