## ✨ Key Features

### ✅ No Azure Account Needed for Learning!
- Options 1-5 in each menu run **locally** (simulated)
- Perfect for studying and debugging
- No cloud costs

### ✅ Deploy to Azure When Ready
- Options 6-8 deploy actual resources
- Reads configuration from `appsettings.json`
- Full Azure SDK integration

### ✅ Visual & Interactive
- Progress indicators (🔄, ✅, ❌)
- Step-by-step execution
- Real-time feedback
- JSON output for debugging

