## 🔧 Configuration

All demos read from `appsettings.json`:

```json
{
  "Azure": {
    "SubscriptionId": "your-subscription-id",
    "ResourceGroup": "rg-az204-compute",
    "Location": "eastus"
  },
  "AppService": {
    "WebAppName": "webapp-az204-9199"
  },
  "Functions": {
    "FunctionAppName": "func-az204-demo",
    "StorageAccountName": "staz204func"
  },
  "ContainerInstances": {
    "ContainerGroupName": "aci-az204-demo",
    "Image": "mcr.microsoft.com/azuredocs/aci-helloworld"
  },
  "AKS": {
    "ClusterName": "aks-az204-demo",
    "NodeCount": 3,
    "NodeVmSize": "Standard_DS2_v2"
  }
}
```

